<item>
            <title>[SOLR-7856] Tidy up exception handling in AngularJS UI</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-7856</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When exceptions occur, the Angular UI can still show a large stack trace rather than a nice error message. The angular UI needs to handle errors in a similar manner to the current UI.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
